                  <div class="headerposts"><h4>noticia anterior</h4></div>
                  <img src="https://www.gasteizhoy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9d53a948-f715-491b-8cb0-37e32ca3c2bd.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="cordón policial buesa" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.gasteizhoy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9d53a948-f715-491b-8cb0-37e32ca3c2bd.jpg 1212w, https://www.gasteizhoy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9d53a948-f715-491b-8cb0-37e32ca3c2bd-350x263.jpg 350w, https://www.gasteizhoy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9d53a948-f715-491b-8cb0-37e32ca3c2bd-879x659.jpg 879w, https://www.gasteizhoy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9d53a948-f715-491b-8cb0-37e32ca3c2bd-150x113.jpg 150w, https://www.gasteizhoy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9d53a948-f715-491b-8cb0-37e32ca3c2bd-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.gasteizhoy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9d53a948-f715-491b-8cb0-37e32ca3c2bd-60x45.jpg 60w, https://www.gasteizhoy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9d53a948-f715-491b-8cb0-37e32ca3c2bd-68x51.jpg 68w, https://www.gasteizhoy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9d53a948-f715-491b-8cb0-37e32ca3c2bd-190x143.jpg 190w" sizes="(max-width: 1212px) 100vw, 1212px" />                  <h3>Cordón policial en el Buesa Arena horas antes del partido</h3>
